Package: duck_connect
Title: Cross-Language Data Sharing with DuckDB
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("DuckData", "Team", , "info@duckdata.dev", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: DuckConnect provides efficient cross-language data sharing 
    using DuckDB as a shared memory database, eliminating expensive 
    push/pull operations between R, Python, and Julia. Includes metadata
    management, access control, and lineage tracking.
